# Routine heartbeat log
# Each cloud routine appends a `<UTC timestamp> <routine-id> started` line BEFORE STEP 0 runs,
# then commits + pushes immediately. This makes silent failures visible:
#   - heartbeat commit + workflow commit → routine completed
#   - heartbeat commit only (no workflow commit) → routine started but died mid-flow
#   - no heartbeat commit → routine never actually executed (infra issue)
# Routine IDs: pm = pre-market, mo = market-open, mid = midday, eod = daily-summary, wr = weekly-review
